org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.plots.datatypes

Class CategoryPlotData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.plots.datatypes.PlotData
      • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.plots.datatypes.CategoryPlotData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, JIPipeData, JIPipeValidatable, JIPipeParameterCollection
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BarCategoryPlotData, BoxAndWhiskerCategoryPlotData, LineCategoryPlotData, StackedBarCategoryPlotData, StatisticalCategoryPlotData

    public abstract class CategoryPlotData
extends PlotData
    Contains data for category plots. Any category plot has following columns: Value (Double), Category (String), Group (String)

    Values are assigned a category that is its X-axis. Colors are assigned by its group
